---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="NotaryTautua - Online Notary Services & Legal Document Authentication"
  description="Professional online notary services, apostille processing, remote online notarization (RON), and international document authentication for individuals and businesses."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">NotaryTautua</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">NotaryTautua</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Online Notary & Legal Documentation Services</h1>
    <p>Your trusted platform for remote online notarization, apostille services, and international legal document authentication.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Remote Online Notarization (RON)</h2>
      <p>Get your documents notarized from anywhere in the world using secure video conferencing. Legal in all 50 U.S. states with tamper-evident digital seals.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Apostille Services</h2>
      <p>Fast apostille processing for documents destined for Hague Convention countries. Birth certificates, diplomas, powers of attorney, and corporate documents.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>International Document Authentication</h2>
      <p>Embassy legalization and authentication services for countries outside the Hague Convention. We handle the full chain of certification for your documents.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Digital Notary & E-Signatures</h2>
      <p>Legally binding electronic notarization with advanced identity verification. Secure document storage, audit trails, and instant delivery of notarized copies.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Real Estate & Loan Closings</h2>
      <p>Mobile and remote notary services for property transactions, mortgage closings, refinancing documents, and title transfers across all jurisdictions.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Legal Document Preparation</h2>
      <p>Professional drafting and notarization of affidavits, sworn statements, powers of attorney, wills, and business formation documents.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>
